songs.title: Zip-a-Dee-Doo-Dah
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus 1]
Zip-a-dee-doo-dah
Zip-a-dee-eh
My, my, my, my, my, what a wonderful day
Plenty of sunshine heading my way
Zip-a-dee-doo-dah
Zip-a-dee-eh

[Verse]
Oh, Mr. Bluebird on my shoulder
It's the truth, and it's actual
Everything is going to be satisfactual

[Chorus 2]
Zip-a-dee-doo-dah
Zip-a-dee-eh
Wonderful feelings
Wonderful day

[Instrumental Bridge]
C'mon
That's right

[Verse]
Oh, Mr. Bluebird on my shoulder
It's the truth, and it's actual
Everything is going to be satisfactual

[Chorus 2]
Zip-a-dee-doo-dah
Zip-a-dee-eh
Wonderful feelings (yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
Wonderful day (one more time now)
Wonderful feelings
Wonderful day

[Outro]
Wonderful feeling, oh yeah
Wonderful day, yeah
What a wonderful day
